      • getServerCandidate

        public IceCandidateInfo getServerCandidate()
        Polls the candidates list maintained by this client to obtain a candidate gathered on the server side. This method blocks until there is a candidate to return. This is a one-time operation for the returned element.
        Returns:
        the gathered candidate, null when interrupted while waiting
